      • AccessContextInitializer

      • AccessContextInitializer

        public AccessContextInitializer(String user,
                                String timestamp)
        Creates a new rule with specified username and timestamp. timestamp is parsed flexibly by DfTypeUtil.
        パラメータ:
        user - the name of current user
        timestamp - the timestamp string 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS'

      • AccessContextInitializer

        public AccessContextInitializer(String user,
                                String timestamp,
                                String process)
        Creates a new rule with specified username, timestamp and processname.
        パラメータ:
        user - the name of current user
        timestamp - the timestamp string 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS'
        process - the name of current process

      • AccessContextInitializer
